eu.webtoolkit.jwt
Class WCssDecorationStyle

java.lang.Object
  eu.webtoolkit.jwt.WCssDecorationStyle

public class WCssDecorationStyle
extends java.lang.Object

A style class for a single widget or style sheet rule.

You can manipulate the decoration style of a single widget using WWidget.getDecorationStyle() or you can use a WCssDecorationStyle to add a rule to the inline style sheet using WCssStyleSheet.addRule(String selector, WCssDecorationStyle style, String ruleName).
